### Creates a new patient entity
POST http://localhost:4000/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria.silva@example.com",
  "address": "456 Oak St, Anytown, USA",
  "dateOfBirth": "1995-05-15",
  "registeredDate": "2024-11-20"
}

